---
title: Garlic & Herb Chicken with Parmesan Veggie Couscous & Mayonnaise
description: It’s fragrant chicken sprinkled with herbs and garlic tonight and it’s calling our name. We’re going to answer to the
call with a colourful couscous, popping with veggies and cheese. When they meet it will be an explosion of flavour.
